line 佈陣 組織 戰術</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365941</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:31:16.000Z","msg":"推 多謝支持 小弟睇漏左呢個post"},{"pid":"56404fcd3126e4ad593b0024d7dc92b0734c0d73","tid":1365961,"uid":74888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:37:40.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"5c8d481a24bb9fa5d36d07e958e857ccd88baa2c","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59ec74dee3b5d4c0b1be77aeae4d553e46c774ee","tid":1365961,"uid":43999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:08:42.000Z","msg":"我係一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>土生土長嘅元朗人</strong></span></span> 亦都係一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>軍事迷</strong></span></span> 加上好熟悉元朗嘅地理環境 我係借朋友acc出post<br />\n<br />\n所以我有D野唔可以唔同你地講 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>希望你地可以睇曬我下面講嘅野</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我係下面<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">會列出我所講嘅論點嘅證據</span></span></strong> 我講嘅野絕對好大機會發生<br />\n<br />\n一、地理環境分析<br />\n遊行路程必經嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗大馬路</span></strong></span>係一個香港版既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">溫泉關</span></span></strong><br />\n溫泉關 係《戰狼三百》斯巴達300人打波斯10萬大軍嘅地方<br />\n究竟點解300人可以打10萬個人？<br />\n就係因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>窄路可以以少打多</strong></span></span> 而且溫泉關 係一個峽谷 斯巴達人當年係峽谷上方部處兵力<br />\n而元朗大馬路隔離嘅樓正正好似溫泉關咁樣 警犬可以係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>每棟樓嘅天台放槍手 催淚彈兵 同天文台</strong></span>(觀察地理環境 作出戰術部處嘅狗)<br />\n對遊行嘅局勢極之不利<br />\n<br />\n二、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大部分</span></strong></span>發夢去元朗嘅人都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔熟悉元朗嘅地理環境</strong></span></span> 同警犬戰術部處<br />\n我睇過好多香港警犬清場嘅片 發夢推斷到大概佢地嘅戰術部處 <br />\n加上佢發出<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對通知書</span></strong></span> 坐實我嘅推斷<br />\n* 係呢part嘅最後我會附上衛星圖同街道圖<br />\n首先 警犬會係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屋頂部處人手</strong></span></span> 等示威者行到去大馬路中間 佢哋就會開始行動<br />\n<br />\n1) 防暴警察會手持長盾 形成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>長盾陣 死守</strong></span>元朗大馬路周圍<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有小路</span></strong>  <br />\n商場會開始落閘 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>鄉黑刀手會混入示威者</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>衝鋒車</strong></span>會進入元朗<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大馬路</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打橫泊</span></strong> 同埋長盾狗配合衝鋒車 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>塞死所有離開元朗嘅路</strong></span> 圍堵所有示威者 方便一網打盡 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>刀手到時候會開始斬人</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n3) 人群會進入恐慌 警犬會開始<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>釋放催淚彈</strong></span> 令所有人想反抗 <br />\n<br />\n4) 長盾狗會開始慢慢<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>收窄我哋嘅活動範圍</strong></span> 因為出左反對通知書 所以佢哋可以名正言順咁打鳩我哋 同埋<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">刀手著黑色衫</span></strong>混入我哋 開始<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打警察</strong></span>(當然係做戲啦) 仲可以順勢話我哋係暴動 長盾狗會時不時放狗入嚟拉人入去長盾陣入面打 跟手拉埋你 元朗狗屋就係正隔離 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勇武嘅人會越嚟越少</strong></span> 剩低和理非 我哋會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>越嚟越難反抗</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n5) 打到一半佢就會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">突然放水比你哋衝</span></strong> 個條路好大可能會係商場入口(目的係要你係人哋眼中睇落係衝擊防線 同埋破壞附近公物) 點解我會覺得好大可能係商場入口 因為我哋走嘅時候會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有機會撞門走</span></strong> 加上刀手著黑色衫攞住刀係我哋隔離繼續做戲 順勢<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>營造暴徒形象</strong></span> 繼續高調拉人低調放刀手 仲可以屈鳩我哋做<br />\n<br />\n6) 由於上述計劃使用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武力嘅程度</span></strong>都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>催淚彈同警棍</strong></span> 所以藍絲一定會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>強調佢哋以最低武力鎮壓暴動</strong></span> 然後社會 會覺得光復元朗係暴動 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">輿論會拉翻走淺黃</span></strong> 到時候我哋就更加難對抗暴政 而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比狗打完嘅和理非翻到屋企就會覺得自己係condom仔</span></span></strong> 我哋會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>開始分化</strong></span> 大陸會開始係連登打文帶風向 黃絲會係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內憂外患底下分裂</span></strong> 變到好似雨傘運動咁<br />\n<br />\n7) 大部分人都係 係香港同九龍出嚟 同埋新界其他地方對元朗嘅地理環境熟悉程度可想而知<br />\n元朗大馬路係得一條直路 遊行嘅人如果有幾萬人係發生武力鎮壓嘅時候係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔會有機會走得切</strong></span><br />\n如果有去過元朗嘅朋友都知 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">D路係窄到仆街</span></strong><br />\n平時去元朗多幾個水貨客都行唔到 更何況到時有幾萬人塞係度<br />\n大馬路又比佢塞左 到時成個元朗<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>得翻西鐵走到 </strong></span>加上如果好彩有其他車 車走你都<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好大機會比人抄牌</strong></span> 留底<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抽後算賬</span></strong></span><br />\n唔好妄想會有元朗居民收留你 以我所知 大馬路附近嘅樓都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好少民居</span></strong> 加上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天台有狗</span></strong> 所以你一上去就會收皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDFnfLd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDFnfLd.png&h=29c7acef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WGwYyyp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWGwYyyp.png&h=03368bfe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>*藍色係狗車會堵塞嘅路段<br />\n衝鋒車擋住龍頭龍尾去路 加上盾兵 壓迫我哋嘅活動空間 困住所有人<br />\n*紅色代表狗部處人手嘅建築物 包括盾兵 槍手 同催淚彈嘅砲手<br />\n佢哋可以用盾狗組成人墻 堵塞所有小路</strong> </span><br />\n<br />\n三、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不過</span></strong></span>我有後著<br />\n雖然如果照原定路線就會收皮 但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我有更加好嘅方法</strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復元朗</span></strong></span>嘅目的係為香港市民<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出一口惡氣</strong></span> 同埋<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喚醒元朗新界區嘅居民 吸納更加多嘅人加入我哋</span></strong> <br />\n其實我有兩個方法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一 將不合作運動升級 係當日長期佔用西鐵線</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>安全表達訴求</ins></span></strong></span> 同埋影響元朗人嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>交通同樓價</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong> 第二 可以按照之前有個巴打提議 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日日申請不反對通知書</span></ins></span></strong> 如果狗個邊出反對通知書 就可以<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重影響元朗區經濟同樓價</span></strong></ins> 班鄉黑見到樓價喺咁跌 每日無啦啦唔見左幾皮野 都幾爽下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">講到呢度 我希望大家三思而後行 我知道大家好嬲 我自己都係 身邊所有人都係 我個日721發夢翻嚟都差D比人打 我個晚睇完 同大家一樣瞓唔著 個日我都想打死曬班冚家產 但係我希望大家可以保留貴軀 保護到自己 又可以搞鳩班鄉黑 班狗又要日日設防係度 真係百利而無一害 我哋可以重新考慮遊行路線 再光復元朗都唔遲</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔想大家光復元朗 而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今次嘅計劃</strong></span>係比灣仔 金鐘 沙田 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>局勢最差</strong></span></span>嘅一次 加上我係連登睇左咁多個post 我感覺到我哋大部分人嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>裝備都唔夠支援我哋嘅行動</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>狗裝備精良</strong></span> 如果可以執行到佢哋嘅劇本 我哋係毫無還手之力 而大部分人已知嘅裝備<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只有黃頭盔 眼罩同豬嘴</span></strong> 頂唔到手臂延伸 更何況衝擊長盾狗或者對付刀手<br />\n<br />\n2) 對方有接受過專業訓練 係佢哋有利嘅環境作戰 只會對我哋更不利<br />\n<br />\n3) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">欠缺大台 無人指揮 無人統一戰術及作出支援</span></strong> 所以我哋勇武嘅人未必有效咁配合<br />\n甚至有可能<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">阻礙到自己人行動</span></strong> 令局勢更加不利 更加容易被狗引導去佢哋想行嘅劇本<br />\n<br />\n4) 香港人體質比較差 即使有更加高級嘅裝備 都未必執行到對付狗或者刀手嘅戰術<br />\n<br />\n5) 我哋接受嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>安全觀念唔夠應付行動</strong></span> 例如大部分post都無講一D自衛方法<br />\n再者比較勇武嘅人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做法觀念無統一(打交方面)</span></strong>配合唔到 所以一定唔夠警犬嚟<br />\n不過我會持續更新自衛方式相關嘅post 同埋分析戰術 希望大家可以幾多人去 幾多人翻嚟 做到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>不流血 不受傷 不被捕</ins></span></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n打到呢度 證明左我嘅誠意 我出post嘅初心係唔希望再見到有人係我面前受傷同犧牲<br />\n希望大家可以推我上去 比更加多人知<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:01:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3b5fbc106bc9f4d59393c9b8d97a10522e7af56","tid":1365961,"uid":261470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:56:18.000Z","msg":"中計?"},{"pid":"92229ba6fdd790398dec3dbf1cab7b00a75cb866","tid":1365961,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:12:12.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"4b5829efd2552d7900c4452cb3febabc2b1c591e","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bcd2fafad3f16cb2d125dff089e8b5bb70bb502","tid":1365961,"uid":43999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:12:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d22599c12108d2036f36f599bd1b0af78771e05","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bcd2fafad3f16cb2d125dff089e8b5bb70bb502","tid":1365961,"uid":43999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:12:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f3c4f398eb38e2fa7dee168bd954b60c8cc3c9e","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bcd2fafad3f16cb2d125dff089e8b5bb70bb502","tid":1365961,"uid":43999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:12:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2197bda76195b002af35a895d6dea3c7f167ab9","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23407c4ea9a41d528c3c22ea2e9284a9f5522c0c","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:13:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"663d1e36eee3d97b9a9ec0c003c93e98fd524dc0","tid":1365961,"uid":229645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}